#: src/2835-project-safe-transmute.md:53
msgid "The safe transmute project group has the following initial scope:"
msgstr ""

#: src/2835-project-safe-transmute.md:55
msgid ""
"to define APIs for allowing zero copy transmute between types in a "
"completely memory safe manner"
msgstr ""

