msgid "Constraints and considerations"
msgstr ""

#: src/2835-project-safe-transmute.md:63
msgid ""
"In its work, the project-group should consider various constraints and "
"considerations:"
msgstr ""

#: src/2835-project-safe-transmute.md:66
msgid "That this feature is meant for performance sensitive workloads"
msgstr ""

#: src/2835-project-safe-transmute.md:67
msgid ""
"That safety is of the upmost importance as there is already a way to "
"transmute using unsafe APIs"
msgstr ""

